                              "peripheral": "OPAMP2_VINP",
                              "help": {
                                "en": [
                                  "1. Remove the heatsink and the thermal interposer to simplify the following two steps.",
                                  "2. Close the two jumpers JP1 and JP2 located on the bottom side of the board in proximity of the shunt resistors.",
                                  " Make sure to close both the jumpers for their entire length to ensure good electrical connection and to avoid malfunctions.",
                                  "3. Disconnect shunt resistors R31, R32, R35 and R36.",
                                  "4. Mount again the heatsink with thermal interposer"
